name: NOT A CULT
description: The project is a Memecoin on Apechain. The CULT represents the NFT class of 2021, when NFTs really took off, and is an ode to their journey. It is an attempt at storytelling and lore building through a memecoin. Different NFT communities can branch out the lore in their own way, thus potentially adding to the lore. CULT had a fair launch using the Ape Express tool (pump fun equivalent) in Apechain.
